This package
============

This package contains experiments on online handwriting recognition, more
specifically for Chinese characters. Currently only Hidden Markov Models are
used but other techniques may be tried in the future.

Requirements
------------

Python       2.4    http://www.python.org
GHMM *       SVN    http://ghmm.sourceforge.net
Tomoe *      SVN    http://tomoe.sourceforge.jp
Tomoe-GTK *  SVN    http://tomoe.sourceforge.jp

[*] The Python bindings are also required.

